message:
The per-turn cost cap (COPILOT_MAX_COST_USD_PER_TURN, default $0.30) tripped 3+ times in the last hour for ${CUSTOMER_LABEL}.

Common causes: a runaway ReAct tool loop (look at @tool_count and @tool_names — if same tool fires 5 times, the model is stuck), an unusually long scenario context, or model misconfiguration (Opus override left on accidentally; check @model field).

If this fires repeatedly without a tool-loop signal, the per-turn cap is likely too tight for the customer's actual workload — bump COPILOT_MAX_COST_USD_PER_TURN by 50% in their Vercel project and re-deploy, then re-evaluate after a day.

@oncall-${CUSTOMER_LABEL}
